    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty. It's in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Come take a look!",
