      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-quality masterpiece. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or imperfections, while every body panel aligns with factory precision. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent persists. Every button, screen, and switch functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history and a pristine engine bay free of any dust or seepage. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
