      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays in pristine, flawless condition. It drives like a total dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is definitely the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
