      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. Critically, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed as preventative maintenance. The chassis retains its original kinematics with factory-spec bushings and dampers, ensuring the legendary 'M' turn-in response. This is a concours-level specimen with a documented service history and zero mechanical compromises.",
